{"pv47:0.1":"Petavatthu ","pv47:0.2":"Mahavagga ","pv47:0.3":"12. Ambavanapetavatthu ","pv47:1.1":"“Ayanca te pokkharani suramma, ","pv47:1.2":"Sama sutittha ca mahodaka ca; ","pv47:1.3":"Supupphita bhamaragananukinna, ","pv47:1.4":"Katham taya laddha ayam manunna. ","pv47:2.1":"Idanca te ambavanam surammam, ","pv47:2.2":"Sabbotukam dharayate phalani; ","pv47:2.3":"Supupphitam bhamaragananukinnam, ","pv47:2.4":"Katham taya laddhamidam vimanam”. ","pv47:3.1":"“Ambapakkam dakam yagu, ","pv47:3.2":"sitacchaya manorama; ","pv47:3.3":"Dhitaya dinnadanena, ","pv47:3.4":"tena me idha labbhati”. ","pv47:4.1":"“Sanditthikam kammam evam passatha, ","pv47:4.2":"Danassa damassa samyamassa vipakam; ","pv47:4.3":"Dasi aham ayyakulesu hutva, ","pv47:4.4":"Sunisa homi agarassa issara”ti. ","pv47:5.1":"Ambavanapetavatthu dvadasamam. "}